section.div: Extended brand repo that can be used with https://github.com/sethcottle/littlelink

LinkStack - the ultimate solution for creating a personalized & professional profile page. Showcase all your important links in one place, forget the limitation of one link on social media. Set up your personal site on your own server with just a few clicks.
Strapi Demo application for Corporate Websites using Next.js

div.div:
Add initial setup for LinkTree app
* **Dependencies**: Add `tailwindcss`, `shadcn-ui`, `framer-motion`, `postcss`, `autoprefixer` to `package.json` * **Scripts**: Add scripts for building and starting the app in `package.json` * **TailwindCSS**: Add `tailwind.config.js` with content paths, custom colors, and `shadcn-ui` plugin * **PostCSS**: Add `postcss.config.js` with `tailwindcss` and `autoprefixer` plugins * **Global Styles**: Add `globals.css` importing TailwindCSS base, components, and utilities * **Layout**: Add `layout.tsx` with `ThemeProvider` and `framer-motion` * **Page**: Add `page.tsx` with links array and functional component using `framer-motion` and `shadcn-ui`
feat(create-turbo): apply package-manager and official-starter transforms, update README.md for w4w monorepo information
